Sweet Treats

'You're back, and with an empty platter at that! You have my gratitude. I don't say that to just anyone; you've made quite a few people smile today.\n\n'Come back tomorrow. There will always be mouths to feed.'
dnt
Deliver Ciriel's pastries to hungry guards ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

'Ah, you there! It appears you have some spare time on your hands. You've seen the guards hard at work around the city, yes? Despite the festival, they keep watch day and night. The war remains fresh on everyone's minds, I'm afraid.

'The guards are busy people with little time, but I want to help them find some enjoyment nevertheless. And food is the key to anyone's heart.

'I've just made a batch of small pastries and let them cool on that table over there. I'll need you to deliver them to any hungry-looking guards nearby. Quickly now! I don't want my pastries to get cold.'
Ciriel's plate of pastries are on the table next to her.\n\nYou will need to take some pastries to distribute among the guards.
dnt
Return to Ciriel
'Many thanks! Could you pass that message on to the chef as well?'
'It saddens me that I cannot join in the celebrations right now, but I appreciate the kind gesture.'
'Thank you, I needed that. It's been a long day, but Ciriel's pastries always taste good.'
'My favourite! If I had to do all of this work just to get a pastry from Ciriel, then it was worth it.'
